OL,3,CMan charged over kidnap and rape of
OL,4,Cteenage girl
OL,6,FPolice have charged a man with the
OL,7,Frape and abduction of a teenage girl
OL,8,Fin an area of Boston.
OL,10,FIt comes after officers were called
OL,11,Fout to Marsh Lane in the town in the
OL,12,Fearly hours of Tuesday morning
OL,13,Ffollowing reports of a serious sexual
OL,14,Fassault by a stranger.
OL,16,FA short while later, a 33-year-old man
OL,17,Fwas arrested at the nearby Lord Grey
OL,18,Fhotel.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
