OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1773876312
OL,3,CMan charged over kidnap and rape of
OL,4,Cteenage girl
OL,6,FJames Savage, also known as Jay
OL,7,FSavage, has since been charged with
OL,8,Frape by penetration of the mouth of a
OL,9,Fteenage girl, child abduction, threats
OL,10,Fwith a bladed article and taking
OL,11,Findecent images.
OL,13,FHe is due to appear at Lincoln
OL,14,FMagistrates Court on Thursday.
OL,16,FLincolnshire Police meanwhile has
OL,17,Furged against online speculation over
OL,18,Fthe alleged assault, warning of the
OL,19,Fdangers of misinformation being spread
OL,20,Fonline.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1773876312
OL,3,CMan charged over kidnap and rape of
OL,4,Cteenage girl
OL,6,FThe force also stressed they were not
OL,7,Flooking for anyone else in connection.
OL,9,FDetective Inspector Claire Rimmer, of
OL,10,FBoston's Protecting Vulnerable People
OL,11,FUnit, said: "This is an investigation
OL,12,Finto an alleged rape in the Boston
OL,13,Farea by somebody unknown to the victim.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
