OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1773876312
OL,3,CMan charged over kidnap and rape of
OL,4,Cteenage girl
OL,6,F"Incidents of this nature, while
OL,7,Funderstandably alarming, are extremely
OL,8,Frare in the county of Lincolnshire.
OL,9,FHowever, thanks to the swift and
OL,10,Fcoordinated efforts of numerous teams
OL,11,Fa suspect was identified and
OL,12,Fapprehended within two hours of the
OL,13,Finitial report.
OL,15,F"We recognise the concern this
OL,16,Fincident may cause within our
OL,17,Fcommunity, and we want to update that
OL,18,Fwe are not looking for anyone else in
OL,19,Fconnection with this matter at this
OL,20,Ftime.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
